org.eclipse.modisco.jee.webapp.webapp23
Interface ServletType

public interface ServletType

A representation of the model object 'Servlet Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Icon
  • Servlet Name
  • Display Name
  • Description
  • Servlet Class
  • Jsp File
  • Init Param
  • Load On Startup
  • Run As
  • Security Role Ref
  • Id

See Also:
